             was indicted for <rs id="t18220911-146-off767" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18220911-146-off767" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18220911-146-off767" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18220911-146-cd768" type="crimeDate">17th of July</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220911-146-off767 t18220911-146-cd768"></join>, one handkerchief, value 4 s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18220911-146-victim1389" type="victimName">
                           David 
                           Richards
                        <interp inst="t18220911-146-victim1389" type="surname" value="Richards"></interp>
